# Python environment (this repo)

- Treat **`./.venv/bin/python`** as the only supported interpreter for local development, tests, and scripts in this repository.
- When running shell commands here, prefer `.venv/bin/python`, `.venv/bin/pip`, and `.venv/bin/pytest` (or `source .venv/bin/activate` first).
- Do not suggest `pip install` to the user’s global/system Python for this project.
- NERSC / cluster instructions may use their own modules; this rule applies to **local** machine workflows unless the user explicitly says otherwise.
